<p align="center">
  <h1 align="center">AWS CostLens</h1>
  <p align="center">
    <strong>AWS Cost Intelligence CLI Tool</strong><br>
    Terminal-based dashboard for AWS cost monitoring, resource scanning, and report generation.
  </p>
</p>

